org.wicketstuff.poi.excel

Interface CellExporter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneralPurposeExporter

    public interface CellExporter
    Function interface to access the component table data and set in the Cell. A general purpose one is provided, but it can be customized by setting TableComponentAsXlsHandler.setCellExporter(CellExporter)
    Author:
    Pedro Santos
